    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      210.35,
      549.78,
      241.97
    ],
    "text": "Police Sergeant 67763 D.G. Ranasinghe Posthumously Promoted to the Rank of Sub-Inspector of Police",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      256.58,
      548.12,
      336.44
    ],
    "text": "Police Sergeant 67763 D.G. Ranasinghe, who was attached to the Kantale Camp of the Special Task Force, tragically lost his life on 12.07.2026 after being swept away by the waters of the Mahaweli River while on an operation to apprehend individuals involved in the illegal transportation of sand in the Mulukkusetti area of the Kinniya Police Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      351.02,
      544.52,
      414.94
    ],
    "text": "In recognition of his service and sacrifice while performing official duties, the Inspector General of Police (IGP) has approved the officer's posthumous promotion from the rank of Police Sergeant to Sub-Inspector of Police, in accordance with the relevant Public Administration Circulars, with effect from 12.07.2026.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      429.4,
      550.83,
      461.14
    ],
    "text": "A photograph of the late officer is attached. The media is kindly requested to publish the above announcement for the information of the public.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
